{"id":236815,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-长沙多位访民因上访被扣押殴打（图）/","date":"2012-07-02T13:31:21Z","modified":"2012-07-02T13:31:21Z","title":"维权网 | 长沙多位访民因上访被扣押殴打（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-oVoiscCm0VY/T_GAiqHjJtI/AAAAAAAAI4Q/avVYC8GBFZ4/s1600/1.jpg\"> </a></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-oVoiscCm0VY/T_GAiqHjJtI/AAAAAAAAI4Q/avVYC8GBFZ4/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"206\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-oVoiscCm0VY/T_GAiqHjJtI/AAAAAAAAI4Q/avVYC8GBFZ4/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-yaFqELOXDIs/T_GAjqZHaKI/AAAAAAAAI4Y/PUCcfdBmJhc/s1600/2.22jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"189\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-yaFqELOXDIs/T_GAjqZHaKI/AAAAAAAAI4Y/PUCcfdBmJhc/s320/2.22jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张成报道）因长沙市众多强制拆迁受害访民的上访被信访局全部终结，多位访民前往北京上访，在北京南站拉出横幅：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>我们的房子找谁要！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日凌晨</span><span>，多位长沙访民被送进久敬庄，随即被强制遣返回长沙。当晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点，访民回到长沙后在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">610</span><span>法制培训基地门口，各辖区负责维稳人员分别把访民们带走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>天心区访民张作明、唐国玉、段静玲、黄美珍被送上另一辆大巴离开，被送到天心区公安分局治安三队。天心区政法委工作人员罗智在现场，他对闻讯赶来的其他访民说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>警告你不要拍照！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张作明、唐国玉、段静玲、黄美珍被关在治安三队，家属要求见面被拒，警方的说法是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>需要询问调查！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>公安给这四人做笔录，笔录内容包括：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>基本情况；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>上访目的；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>要求条件；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>上访组织人；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>到京的过程；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>到京的联系人；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>火车站事情；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>上访的部门。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>家属质疑说，上访你们公安要调查什么，房子被强拆怎么不立案调查？治安大队有何职能，他可以对上访人员进行处理吗，上访到底是违法还是受到法律保护？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>早上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8.30</span><span>分，岳麓区荣弯镇的访民李岱旭（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18975893128</span><span>）在电话中称：昨天晚上有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>名访民被街道接访人员拖下大巴车后，被抛到野郊。遭遇到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>名不明身份人员殴打，受害人已经在捞刀河派出所报案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>，天心区的访民张应辉也在电话中说，她也被关在治安三队，限制了人身自由，儿子去接她，被警察打倒在地，拨打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报警警方也不出警。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>点，被关押的访民王清云（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15974278428</span><span>）对外传出消息：访民周美玲在长沙治安三大队因言语与警察争吵突然发病晕倒。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>上午，长沙芙蓉区上访人员刘晋武、谭海艳、陈平在长沙下火车时被长沙县跳马乡司法所工作人员暴打。长沙跳马乡访民李巧玲刚下火车被不明身份人员控制，在长沙市车站路派出所等待处理。李巧玲此前连续</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>次从北京上访回来后被拘留。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>相关报道请参见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/06/blog-post_522.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/06/blog-post_522.html</a></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-6290363380764419185?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/b756f2ff1.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}